  <name>ZQuest Classic</name>
  <summary>ZQuest Classic is a game engine for creating games similar to the popular classic adventure game.</summary>
  <description>
    <p>ZQuest Classic started as a classic 80s-style dungeon-crawler game engine, that over time has grown into a more modern engine. It allows much easier creation of dungeon-crawler style games than other big game engines, due to the number of features that are available without the need for any form of programming knowledge.</p>
  </description>
